parametersDescriptions.defaultValue: The default value. Use when the component is not controlled.
parametersDescriptions.onChange: Callback invoked when new value is being set.
parametersDescriptions.selectionFollowsFocus: If true the selected tab changes on focus. Otherwise it only changes on activation.
parametersDescriptions.value: The value of the currently selected Tab. If you don't want any selected Tab, you can set this prop to false.

returnValueDescriptions.contextValue: Returns the values to be passed to the tabs provider.
